I'm baaaack!

::Ratchet and Bluestrwak get up and head out to the ark::
Ratchet: Whoa.
::Bluestreak looks to Prowl::
Bluestreak: What happened?
Ratchet: Whatever happened I'll fix it.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

::Soundwave wakes up::
Soundwave: Vulois, come in.  I am fully functional and await your orders.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

::Ramjet, Dirge and Skywarp wake up::
Ramjet: Alright Destrocons, I say we contact Magmatron and join the Destrons.
Skywarp: Why should we trust him?
Dirge: Destruction, destruction is always good.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

::Onyx flys to Defection::
Onyx: I'm with you too Defection.  What happened?
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

::Galvatron wakes up peacefully.  he turns on his internal computer::
Computer: You have been asleep for five days.  Nemises is 24 solar cycles 
away.
Galvatron: FIVE DAYS?
